title: Inside Passenger Jet Vol.1
description: This is a sample pack consisting of authentic recordings of various stages of the flight of an Airbus 320 passenger aircraft.
longDescription:
DEMO SOUND

Here you will find wav files and loops that can be used to create an endless sound of the atmosphere inside a passenger jet.

"Inside Passenger Jet Vol.1" will become an indispensable assistant for multimedia content creators, computer game developers and those who like to experiment with sound. Immerse yourself in the atmosphere of a real flight with this unique set of sounds!

All sounds are recorded in WAV format, 96 kHz/24Bit.


Inside Passenger Jet Vol.1 - Sound List
technicalDetails:
Number of Audio Waves: 40

Number of Audio Cues: 40

Sample rate / bit rate: 96000 Hz

Do Sound FX loop: Yes

Minutes of audio provided: 99 min

Windows: Yes
